logs.description: Te hītori whiriwhiringa whānui me te tātari matatau, nga āheinga kaweake, me nga huarahi tirotiro.
logs.title: Ngā Rārangi Whakawhitinga

management.description: Te tirotiro whiriwhiringa katoa me te rakerake ririki, te whakatatū, me nga āheinga whakahaere whakawhiti.
management.title: Whakahaere Whakawhitinga

management.description: Fa'atere atoa i te tere ora o te ta'ata e te mau mea atoa mai te fa'a'ite atura, te fa'amaora'a, te fa'aatura'a 'ohipa, e te mau ra'a fa'anahora'a i te 'ohipa piha'a no te fa'atere atoa i te ta'ata fa'ahohora'a.
management.title: Ta'ata Fa'ahohora'a

tracking.description: Te whakahaere UTXO matatau me te wetewete kauwhata whiriwhiringa me nga ahuatanga tiaki-tūmataiti.
tracking.title: Aroturuki UTXO

management.description: Te whakahaere putea moni-maha me te aroturuki toenga, nga mana haumarutanga, me te whakahaere penapena.
management.title: Whakahaere Pūkete

logs.description: Aroturukihia nga tono tango me te aroturuki tūnga, nga mahinga whakamana, me te whakamanatanga ūhanga.
logs.title: Ngā Rēkoata Tango

management.description: Te whakahaere pūnaha tango whānui me te tukatuka aunoa, te aukati tinihanga, me nga mana ūhanga.
management.title: Whakahaere Tango

methods.description: Whakaahuahia nga kōwhiringa tango tae atu ki nga whakawhiti peeke, nga tangohanga crypto, me nga kaitukatuka-whai-toru.
methods.title: Ngā Tikanga Tango

trading.title: Fakatau
trading.description: 'Oku 'oatu 'a e ngaahi fa'unga fakatau lahi mo e ngaahi me'angāue fa'u fa'unga fakatatau, ko e fa'ahinga 'o e maketi 'i he taimi totonu, mo e ngaahi me'angāue fakahinohino fa'akalasi kotoa pē ma'a e ngaahi koloa kotoa pē.

spot.title: Fakatau Spot
spot.description: Fai 'a e ngaahi fekau fakatau mo fakatau 'i he taimi ni 'i he ngaahi pa'anga maketi 'o e taimi ni mo e ngaahi ongo fehokotaki lahi, ngaahi sāti loloto, mo e ngaahi me'angāue fakatau fakahinohino.

binary.title: Ngaahi Fili Ua
binary.description: Fakatau 'a e ngaahi fili ua mo e ngaahi analytics fakapolopola, ngaahi me'angāue pule'i mā'olunga, mo e fakahinohino 'o e taimi ma'a e ngaahi founga fakatau 'oku ma'u taimi.

forex.title: Forex
forex.description: Ma'u 'a e ngaahi maketi fetongi pa'anga māmani mo e fakahokohoko MetaTrader 4/5, ngaahi sāti lahi, mo e fakahinohino 'i he kulāsí tulutulu.

p2p.title: Fetongi P2P
p2p.description: Kau ki he fakatau cryptocurrency malu 'a e kakai taki taha mo e malu'i escrow, ngaahi founga totongi felefeleaki, mo e ngaahi pa'anga fakataimi'i.

portfolio.title: Pūtea Whakahaere
portfolio.description: Te rārangi whakahaere pūtea whānui mō te aroturuki i ngā rawa, te wetewete i te whakatutukitanga, me te whakahaere i ō tāhua pūtea puta noa i ngā papaaho katoa.

wallet.title: Whakahaere Pūkoro
wallet.description: Te pūkoro moni-maha haumaru me te aroturuki taurangi wā-tūturu, te hītori whakawhitinga, me ngā āheinga tuku/tango māmā.

transactions.title: Hītori Whakawhitinga
transactions.description: Ngā pūrongo whakawhitinga whakamārama me te tātari tāupe, ngā āheinga kaweake, me ngā huarahi arotake whānui mō ngā mahi pūtea katoa.

transfers.title: Ngā Whakawhitinga
transfers.description: Ngā ratonga whakawhiti ā-roto, ā-waho me te tukatuka tere, ngā utu whakataetae, me te tautoko moni-maha.

investments.title: Ngā Haumi
investments.description: Ngā whai wāhi haumi kanorau me ngā wetewete taumata ngaio, ngā taputapu aromatawai tūraru, me te aroturuki whakatutukitanga puta noa i ngā ahumomo rawa maha.

plans.title: Ngā Mahere Haumi
plans.description: Ngā rautaki haumi kua kohikohia me ngā kōtaha tūraru whakamārama, ngā raraunga whakatutukitanga ō-mua, me ngā kupu pīataata kia ōrite ki ō whāinga pūtea.

staking.title: Ngā Utu Tūnga
staking.description: Whiwhi moni pūmau mā te tūnga matihiko me ngā reiti APY whakataetae, ngā wā raka pīataata, me te tuari utu aunoa.

ico.title: Ngā Hokonga Tohu
ico.description: Te urunga moata ki ngā Taonga Moni Tuatahi kua tirotirohia me ngā pūrongo tūtohutanga whānui, te wetewete ahupūtea-tohu, me te aroturuki haumi.

marketplace.title: Maakete
marketplace.description: Tirotirohia ngā maakete matihiko me te tinana kounga me ngā whakawhitinga haumaru, ngā kaihoko kua whakaūngia, me te tiaki kaihoko whānui.

nft.title: Whare Pukapuka NFT
nft.description: Kimihia, hangaia, me te tauhoko i ngā rawa matihiko ahurei i tō mātou maakete NFT kua kohikohia me ngā āheinga huihui me ngā moni āwhina kaihanga.

store.title: Toa
store.description: Te maakete kounga e whakaatu ana i ngā hua matihiko me te tinana me te tukatuka utu haumaru, te tuku puta noa i te ao, me te tiaki kaihoko.

services.title: Ngā Ratonga
services.description: Ngā ratonga ngaio me ngā taputapu hei whakapai i tō wheako tauhoko, tae atu ki ngā hōtaka hoa, ngā rauemi mātauranga, me te tautoko kounga.

affiliate.title: Hōtaka Hoa
affiliate.description: Whiwhi moni mō tō whatunga mā tō mātou hōtaka hoa whānui me ngā komihi whakataetae, te aroturuki wā-tūturu, me ngā taputapu hokohoko.

support.title: Pokapū Tautoko
support.description: Te tautoko kiritaki ngaio me te whakahaere tikiti, ngā āheinga kōrerorero ora, me te whakahaere pūkete motuhake mō ngā kaiwhakamahi kounga.

faq.title: Puna Mātauranga
faq.description: Ngā tuhinga whānui, ngā akoranga, me ngā pātai auau hei āwhina i a koe ki te whakanui i ngā āheinga papaaho.

insights.title: Ngā Tirohanga
insights.description: Te wetewete maakete ngaio, ngā tirohanga tauhoko, me ngā kōrero ahumahi mai i tō mātou rōpū tohunga pūtea me ngā kairangahau maakete.
